{
  "stem": "2713.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, we took the risk, and we went back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went back home because we had there everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided that we will sell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever is there we will sell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not allowed to do it, but there were plenty of Poles that wanted to buy, especially goods like we had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- everyone wanted to buy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we sold whatever we had in the place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we tried to make Polish documents for us and every one of who had a Polish document.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were just-- they were not 100% because you couldn't be registered anywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the risk you had to take.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we paid a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The underground was making those things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We paid a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the time came that we had to go back because the Germans-- we could see what's happening again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going to clean everyone out from the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- Where were you at this stage with your false-- you had false papers?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were just having them with us, the papers-- if something have happen so that we--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still at home, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had the papers always with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If something happen, we can run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is what had happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister was already-- wasn't home already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Two of my sisters were not home anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the sister that I've got now, which is here in Sydney-- she was-- till the end of the war, she was a maid working for someone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she lived through the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she had a very hard time because with the Poles, it wasn't so easy, and she was a maid for the Poles.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
